//   inventing dB / ms / SNR and WITHOUT pasting Q20i ANC-ON stopwatch rows as
//   this sample's own numbers.
// Vendor anchors: soundcore.com/products/soundcore-q11i · support.soundcore.com
//   Q11i FAQ · recall check 2026-07-24.
// Wave headphones (over-ear). Physics envelope enforced (§8). §7.5 adapted for
//   over-ear / on-ear: A = full-unit weight (no buds/case split); B = playtime
//   @50% (no ANC modes on this SKU); C/E case steps = N/A (no charging case);
//   D/F = USB-C full + quick charge on the unit; G = BT range; H = multipoint;
//   I = passive isolation qualitative only (ANC = None — no invented dB);
//   J = mic qualitative (no SNR); K = codecs in Soundcore App; L = latency
//   qualitative (no ms).
// Sibling ladder: Q11i (A3005, no ANC, this file) → Q20i (A3004, hybrid ANC +
//   soft pouch) → Life Q30 (A3028, Transport/Indoor/Outdoor + hard case) →
//   Space Q45 (A3040, Adaptive ANC + LDAC). Sibling files intentionally untouched.
